            Flowp
    ~ Bringing best ideas from Ruby world to Python ~


What is flowp ?

Flowp is a set of handy libraries / modules which should makes working 
with Python more enjoyable and productive.

For now flowp contains:

    - flowp.testing - better testing framework (BDD, influenced by RSpec) [ready to use]
    - flowp.ftypes - better data structures / types processing / methods chains
    - flowp.system - better files / process manipulation / building system
